00:35:55.470 --> 00:35:58.859
Your digital presence
is the front door to your business.

00:35:58.860 --> 00:36:02.249
If it's closed to some,
it's closed to too many.

00:36:02.250 --> 00:36:05.699
Accessibility is the key
that opens that door.

00:36:05.700 --> 00:36:09.239
Test thoroughly, remove barriers,
and design with empathy,

00:36:09.240 --> 00:36:11.549
because accessibility is ongoing,

00:36:11.550 --> 00:36:14.159
a continual commitment
to ensuring everyone

00:36:14.160 --> 00:36:16.349
